<div><head>《陳留風俗傳》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.2">小黃縣者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.3">宋地黃鄉也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.4">沛公起兵野戰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.5">喪皇妣於黃鄉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.6">天下平定，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.7">乃使使者以梓宮招魂幽野，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.8">於是丹蛇在水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.9">自酒躍入於梓宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.10">其浴處有遺髮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-1a.11">故諡曰昭靈夫人。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-2a.2">浚儀有師曠倉頡城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1690_CHANT_001-2a.3">城上有列仙吹臺。<lb/></seg>
</p>
